OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1782238703
OL,3,CTeenage boy arrested after body found
OL,4,Cin search for missing girl
OL,6,FA 14-year-old boy has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder after a body was
OL,8,Ffound in Blaina, near Ebbw Vale, late
OL,9,Fon Monday 22 June.
OL,11,FThe teenager, from the Blaenau Gwent
OL,12,Farea, is currently in police custody.
OL,14,FFormal identification has not yet
OL,15,Ftaken place but the family of Lilly,
OL,16,Faged 14, who had been reported as
OL,17,Fmissing, has been informed.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
