OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1782238703
OL,3,CTeenage boy arrested after body found
OL,4,Cin search for missing girl
OL,6,FSenior Investigating Officer,
OL,7,FDetective Chief Inspector Steven
OL,8,FThomas, said: "We continue to have a
OL,9,Fsignificant police presence in the
OL,10,Farea and understand the concern
OL,11,Famongst our communities at this time.
OL,13,F"Our enquiries are ongoing to
OL,14,Festablish the circumstances
OL,15,Fsurrounding the death and we currently
OL,16,Fhave one person in police custody
OL,17,Fbeing questioned.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
