PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1782238703
OL,3,CTeenage boy arrested after body found
OL,4,Cin search for missing girl
OL,6,F"I'm asking anyone with information to
OL,7,Fplease come and speak with us, you can
OL,8,Fdo this in person, or you can contact
OL,9,Fus on the usual channels.
OL,11,F"I'd also encourage people not to
OL,12,Fspeculate online as this is a live
OL,13,Finvestigation and such comments can
OL,14,Fhave an impact on our ability to bring
OL,15,Fanyone, found to have committed a
OL,16,Fcriminal offence, to justice."
OL,18,FGwent Police says it has referred the
OL,19,Fincident to the Independent Office for
OL,20,FPolice Conduct (IOPC) "in line with
OL,21,Fnormal procedures".
